NDRTool is the core of NDR Framework.

This application has a microservice architecture that relies on PlayFramework. It runs from a single JAR file with a self-contained application server.

PlayFramework 2.3.8
Apache Fuseki Server 2.3.0
Apache Jena 3.0

========================================

